            "notes": "The deck revolves around the synergy between sacrificing creatures and generating tokens to create a powerful board presence. Prossh, Skyraider of Kher acts as the commander, allowing for quick token generation when casting him from the command zone. Cards like Goblin Bombardment and Purphoros, God of the Forge provide additional value when sacrificing creatures, while cards like Mayhem Devil and Marionette Apprentice punish opponents for each sacrificed creature. The deck also includes various mana ramp cards like Birds of Paradise and Farseek to ensure a fast and consistent mana base. Overall, the key strategy is to generate tokens and sacrifice them for value, overwhelming opponents with a combination of aggression and synergy."
